window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Daniel was Gifted by the gods at birth, able to heal with a touch even the most grievous wounds. Born in a mining camp, he's unable to still his restless heart and journeys to a nearby dungeon town to take his first steps as an Adventurer. Follow his journey in a world filled with monsters, dungeons, and a leveling system. </p> <p>A traditional fantasy story with LitRPG elements. </p>"; 
